233
01:55:19,292 --> 01:55:46,510
We've all seen this, it's happened in neighboring states. Why do we feel as though we're impervious to the same situation or the same circumstances? Because we're not, we're not. So we're in a place where kids are afraid to go to school. And we're also in a place where we see embarrassing news story after embarrassing news story after embarrassing news story in the headlines with the word mentioned.

234
01:55:47,500 --> 01:56:14,275
