284
02:18:56,152 --> 02:19:15,299
Um, we need to, we need to be serious about that. We need to be serious that about funding and to realize that there is a funding issue. Um, and that, that, that effect that the problem is trickling down to our hallways into our classrooms and, um,

285
02:19:16,049 --> 02:19:34,787
